 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search Real Estate Agent The Margolis Team Inc Superior, CO Job details Salary $55,000 - $115,000 a year Job Type Full-time Full Job Description Real Estate Agent - Adams, Boulder, Broomfield, and Weld Counties 
Guarantee your success by joining The Margolis Team Inc.! Focus on an opportunity that offers training, leads, coaching, systems, and fun. We are a small yet powerful team that helps one another succeed. 
NEW REAL ESTATE SALES AGENTS ENCOURAGED TO APPLY! Experienced agents too that want to meet their goals!
 TRAINING:  We offer world-class training. We have a dedicated Team Leader who works with you one on one plus our team leader is a Real Estate Coach for one of the top Coaching companies in the country. When you work with The Margolis Team, you receive 1 on 1 training plus access to the coaching company at no charge. Don't get lost in a crowd within an office of 100+ agents. Work on a small team that cares about you, your goals, and your dreams. We will help you thrive. 
LEADS:  On your first day you will have access to a lead bank of over 1,000 leads. This isn't a phone book thrown on your desk as many companies will offer you, but 1,000 leads that have made an inquiry on a house to purchase at some time. PLUS we receive 20-40 new opportunities EVERY MONTH! You will need to be organized. 
SYSTEMS, Systems, Systems:  Leads and training will only get you so far. Without systems on how to properly manage the leads, an agent's chances for success will quickly dwindle. From a CRM that is the best in the business to automation and artificial intelligence. The Margolis Team is a team that utilizes technology to help you work less and make more money. 
Realistically earn $65,000+ in the first 12 months! 
 
