Responsibilities: 
Have Fun!
 Consult with Clients in order to discover what they are looking for in their dream home; then find properties that meet those needs and show the homes. 
Participate in Zoom Calls and appointments 
Participate in open houses, networking activities to enhance your sales. 
Present purchase offers to sellers and gets buyers under the agreement. We will handle all the administrative work. 
Consistently network and market to prospect for new customers. 
Guide 18 to 50 buyer clients through the home purchase process each year. 
"Always be consulting" by providing your clients with your very best service and your very best advice. 
Present and discuss strategic master marketing plan. 
Have a great daily schedule. 
 
